Go to https://devcenter.heroku.com/articles/heroku-cli
and install heroku cli.
Go to terminal and "heroku -v" to check if working.
Then "heroku login", enter email and password.
Chances are this step may fail on your machine,
if you are behind a firewiall that requires use of proxy to connect to http services.
For that you can set an environement variable 
"export HTTP_PROXY=http://proxy.server.com:1234"
after that try relogging in.
